<i>♪ Don't know what's in store</i>
<i>But together we can open any door ♪</i>

30:41.005 --> 30:43.049
<i>♪ Just to do what's good for you ♪</i>

30:43.508 --> 30:46.052
<i>♪ I'll inspire you a little bit higher  ♪</i>

